	<article class="post-590828 post type-post status-publish hentry category-financial-services category-ipoofferings category-legal tag-china tag-china-securities-regulatory-commission tag-communist-party-of-china tag-initial-public-offerings tag-shenzhen-china tag-xi-jinping per-xi-jinping des-initial-public-offerings org-china-securities-regulatory-commission org-communist-party-of-china geo-china geo-shenzhen-china" id="post-590828">
	<header class="postHeader">
